lyrics:
[verse]
In Feytopya, when the rain pours down
A wooden sauna stands, ready to astound
Burning hot, flames dancing in delight
Inviting us in, safe from the storm's bite

[chorus]
Oh, come and join, let the worries stray
In the cozy sauna, let's find our way
Feel the heat embrace, as the cold winds blow
In Feytopya's sauna, the spirits will glow
